| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6038 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1bd19e8c-ce14-5e2f-9a79-d642a9259da2"
